title: Gloria Estefan - The Party Time Megamix
description:
Gloria Estefan - The Party Time Megamix

Released in 1998, as a limited promo in Target stores only for the Gloria! album.
Now considered extremely rare by collectors.

Featured songs:
Dr. Beat
Conga
I'm Not Giving You Up
You'll Be Mine (Party Time)
Rhythm Is Gonna Get You
1, 2, 3
Get On Your Feet
Everlasting Love
Turn The Beat Around

**  **  **

File is 192 Kbit MP3, with artwork.
Single file contains complete mix.
